Description: Development toolbox for DDE File Manager
 System tray icon and context menu plugins for Deepin File Manager.
 Provides quick access to development tools including Git utilities,
 DEB package building, project downloading, and system configuration.
 .
 This package replaces the old dfm-tools-plugins meta-package and consolidates
 all plugins into a single, extensible architecture with JSON-based configuration
 and system tray integration.
